sof:nodedotjs a sof:Tag ;
    rdfs:label "node.js" ;
    rdfs:comment "Node.js is an event-based, non-blocking, asynchronous I/O runtime that uses Google's V8 JavaScript engine and libuv library. It is used for developing applications that make heavy use of the ability to run JavaScript both on the client as well as on the server side and therefore benefit from the re-usability of code and the lack of context switching." ;
